---
import heroImage from '../assets/rera_lawyer_hero.png';
---

<section class="service-detail-section">
	<div class="service-detail-container">
		<!-- Hero Image -->
		<div class="service-hero">
			<img 
				src={heroImage.src} 
				alt="RERA Lawyer in Noida" 
			/>
		</div>

		<!-- Main Content and Sidebar -->
		<div class="service-content-wrapper">
			<!-- Main Content -->
			<div class="service-main-content">
				<h1>RERA Lawyer in Noida</h1>
				
				<p class="intro-text">
					The Real Estate Regulatory Authority (RERA) was established to balance builder commitments and homebuyer rights. When developers delay flat possessions, charge unauthorized fees, or fail to deliver promised amenities, our specialized RERA lawyers in Noida offer aggressive advocacy before UP-RERA to recover your investments and enforce compliance.
				</p>

				<h2>What We Handle</h2>
				<ul class="service-features">
					<li>
						<strong>Delayed Possession Claims:</strong> Legal action under RERA Section 18 to compel builders to hand over flats and pay monthly interest compensation
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Full Investment Refunds:</strong> Complete recovery of buyer capital with compounding interest due to structural delays or project defaults
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Filing UP-RERA Complaints:</strong> Meticulous drafting and representation before the UP-RERA Adjudication Bench in Noida and Greater Noida
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Execution of RERA Orders:</strong> Filing execution applications and coordination with District Magistrates to enforce cash recovery certificates
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Project Approvals Vetting:</strong> Comprehensive due diligence verifying RERA registration status, land clearance, and escrow account records
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Layout Modification Litigations:</strong> Representation against builders who change architectural layouts or flat specifications without consent
					</li>
				</ul>

				<h2>Why Choose Our Firm</h2>
				<p>
					Builder-buyer disputes require persistent pressure and a complete command over the RERA Act, 2016. Our advocates are uniquely qualified by offering:
				</p>
				<ul class="benefits-list">
					<li>Comprehensive legal expertise in UP-RERA rules, case laws, and appellate processes</li>
					<li>Proven track record of securing heavy compensation, interest awards, and refunds</li>
					<li>Aggressive liaisoning at DM and revenue offices for fast execution of recovery certificates</li>
					<li>Extensive representation before the RERA Appellate Tribunal and High Court</li>
					<li>Defense for homebuyer groups against insolvent developers or stalled projects</li>
				</ul>

				<h2>Our Approach</h2>
				<p>
					We protect the hard-earned lifetime savings of home buyers by enforcing strict developer accountability. We:
				</p>
				<ol class="approach-list">
					<li>Analyze Builder-Buyer Agreements (BBA), payment receipts, bank loans, and builder notices</li>
					<li>Submit structured complaints (Form M or N) on the online UP-RERA portal with proper details</li>
					<li>Represent client interests confidently in all RERA bench hearings and mediation boards</li>
					<li>Refute developer claims regarding force majeure, weather, or government delays</li>
					<li>Secure binding, favorable orders for interest, possession, or complete refunds</li>
					<li>Actively pursue execution petitions if builders delay compliance with the decree</li>
				</ol>

				<h2>Enforce Builder Accountability</h2>
				<p>
					If you are struggling with a delayed flat possession, hidden costs, or builder defaults in Noida, we can help you with:
				</p>
				<ul class="complaint-list">
					<li>Drafting and sending formal pre-complaint legal notices to builders</li>
					<li>Filing fresh complaints for delayed possession before UP-RERA</li>
					<li>Filing execution applications for unfulfilled RERA decrees and recovery citations</li>
					<li>Representing you in the RERA Appellate Tribunal in Lucknow or Greater Noida</li>
				</ul>

				<div class="cta-section">
					<p>Is your developer delaying your flat registry or possession in Noida? Contact us to secure your investment under RERA.</p>
					<a href="/contact" class="cta-button">Get Legal Help</a>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Sidebar Services Links -->
			<aside class="service-sidebar">
				<div class="sidebar-box">
					<h3>Our Services</h3>
					<nav class="services-nav">
						<a href="/cyber-lawyers" class="service-link">
							Cyber Crime Lawyer
						</a>
						<a href="/criminal-lawyers" class="service-link">
							Criminal Lawyer
						</a>
						<a href="/corporate-lawyers" class="service-link">
							Corporate & Industrial Disputes
						</a>
						<a href="/consumer-lawyers" class="service-link">
							Consumer Protection Lawyer
						</a>
						<a href="/civil-lawyers" class="service-link">
							Civil Lawyer
						</a>
						<a href="/property-registration" class="service-link">
							Property Registration
						</a>
						<a href="/notary-lawyer" class="service-link">
							Notary Lawyer
						</a>
						<a href="/rera-lawyer" class="service-link active">
							RERA Lawyer
						</a>
					</nav>
				</div>
			</aside>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.service-detail-section {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #f0f4f8 100%);
		padding: 2rem 1rem 4rem;
		min-height: 100vh;
	}

	.service-detail-container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	/* Hero Image */
	.service-hero {
		width: 100%;
		height: 400px;
		border-radius: 12px;
		overflow: hidden;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);
	}

	.service-hero img {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		object-fit: cover;
	}

	/* Content Wrapper */
	.service-content-wrapper {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px;
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	/* Main Content */
	.service-main-content h1 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 900;
		color: #0f172a;
		margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
		line-height: 1.2;
	}

	.service-main-content h2 {
		font-size: 1.6rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		color: #0f172a;
		margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem 0;
		line-height: 1.3;
	}

	.intro-text {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: #475569;
		line-height: 1.8;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.service-main-content p {
		color: #475569;
		line-height: 1.7;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-size: 1rem;
	}

	.service-features,
	.benefits-list,
	.complaint-list {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
	}

	.service-features li,
	.benefits-list li,
	.complaint-list li {
		padding: 0.75rem 0 0.75rem 2rem;
		position: relative;
		color: #475569;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.service-features li::before,
	.benefits-list li::before,
	.complaint-list li::before {
		content: "→";
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		color: #0ea5a4;
		font-weight: bold;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}

	.service-features li strong {
		color: #0f172a;
	}

	.approach-list {
		padding-left: 2rem;
		color: #475569;
		line-height: 1.7;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.approach-list li {
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
		color: #475569;
	}

	.approach-list li::marker {
		color: #0ea5a4;
		font-weight: bold;
	}

	/* CTA Section */
	.cta-section {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fffe 0%, #e0f7f6 100%);
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		margin-top: 2.5rem;
		border-left: 4px solid #0ea5a4;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.cta-section p {
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		color: #0f172a;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	.cta-button {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
		background: #0ea5a4;
		color: white;
		text-decoration: none;
		border-radius: 8px;
		font-weight: 700;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(14, 165, 164, 0.2);
	}

	.cta-button:hover {
		background: #0d8e8d;
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(14, 165, 164, 0.3);
	}

	/* Sidebar */
	.service-sidebar {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.sidebar-box {
		background: white;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
		position: sticky;
		top: 100px;
		height: fit-content;
	}

	.sidebar-box h3 {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		color: #0f172a;
		margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
		padding-bottom: 1rem;
		border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
	}

	/* Services Navigation */
	.services-nav {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.5rem;
	}

	.service-link {
		display: block;
		padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
		color: #475569;
		text-decoration: none;
		border-radius: 6px;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		border-left: 3px solid transparent;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}

	.service-link:hover {
		background: #f0fffe;
		color: #0ea5a4;
		border-left-color: #0ea5a4;
		transform: translateX(4px);
	}

	.service-link.active {
		background: #f0fffe;
		color: #0ea5a4;
		border-left-color: #0ea5a4;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	/* Responsive Design */
	@media (max-width: 1024px) {
		.service-content-wrapper {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 280px;
		}

		.service-main-content h1 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.service-hero {
			height: 300px;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.service-detail-section {
			padding: 1.5rem 1rem 3rem;
		}

		.service-content-wrapper {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 1.5rem;
		}

		.sidebar-box {
			position: static;
		}

		.service-main-content h1 {
			font-size: 1.6rem;
		}

		.service-main-content h2 {
			font-size: 1.3rem;
		}

		.service-hero {
			height: 250px;
			margin-bottom: 2rem;
		}

		.services-nav {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
			gap: 0.5rem;
		}

		.service-link {
			font-size: 0.9rem;
			padding: 0.6rem 0.75rem;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 480px) {
		.service-detail-section {
			padding: 1rem;
		}

		.service-main-content h1 {
			font-size: 1.3rem;
		}

		.service-main-content h2 {
			font-size: 1.1rem;
			margin-top: 1.75rem;
		}

		.service-hero {
			height: 200px;
			margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		}

		.intro-text {
			font-size: 1rem;
		}

		.cta-section {
			padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
		}

		.services-nav {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.sidebar-box {
			padding: 1rem;
		}
	}
</style>
